<p>Dear <%= @user_name %>,</p>

<p>As a reminder, your Dryad data submission titled, "<%= @resource.title %>" is currently in "Private for peer review" status and has not entered our curation process. If your related manuscript is still in the peer review process, you may ignore this email.</p>

<p>If your related article has been accepted, or if you are ready to initiate the curation process and proceed to publication, please follow these steps:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Login to <a href="https://datadryad.org">https://datadryad.org</a></li>
  <li>Click on “My datasets”</li>
  <li>Click “Update” on your dataset</li>
  <li>On the final page of the submission form (Review and submit page), uncheck the checkbox for "Private for peer review"</li>
  <li>Click "Submit"</li>
</ol>

<p>If your related article has been rejected or you will not be proceeding with the submission of this dataset, kindly contact us at <a href="mailto:<%= @helpdesk_email %>"><%= @helpdesk_email %></a> and we will withdraw your submission.</p>

<p>The Dryad Team</p>
